523
00:25:03,837 --> 00:25:05,739 line:-2
I like the couches
at Apple Park,


524
00:25:05,739 --> 00:25:08,709 line:-2
so I open my Mac and browse
to Furniture Site in Safari


525
00:25:08,709 --> 00:25:11,311 line:-1
to find some similar styles.


526
00:25:11.311 --> 00:25:12.980 line:-1 align:center
As soon as I connect,


527
00:25:12.980 --> 00:25:16.617 line:-2 align:center
Furniture Site
