532
00:25:27,561 --> 00:25:30,297 line:-2
gathers information about me
to share with data brokers.


533
00:25:32.299 --> 00:25:35.502 line:-2 align:center
Furniture Site contributes
the data about my couch browsing


534
00:25:35,502 --> 00:25:38,071 line:-2
and my IP address is used
to combine all of the other


535
00:25:38,071 --> 00:25:41,775 line:-2
bits of data collected
about me from many other places.


536
00:25:41,775 --> 00:25:44,077 align:center
When combined,
the bits and pieces form


537
00:25:44,077 --> 00:25:46,647 line:0
a comprehensive profile
about what I do on the web.


538
00:25:49.049 --> 00:25:51.919 line:-2 align:center
Adding it all together,
the profile that is built


539
00:25:51,919 --> 00:25:55,022 line:-2
represents a very personal
and up-to-date snapshot about


540
00:25:55.022 --> 00:25:58.959 line:-2 align:center
who I am and what's going
on in my life right now.


541
00:25:58,959 --> 00:26:01,695 line:-2
My profile even includes
