545
00:26:09.336 --> 00:26:12.372 line:-2 align:center
intentionally or wanted it
to be shared.


546
00:26:12.372 --> 00:26:14.441 line:-2 align:center
This kind of browsing
history can't be cleared


547
00:26:14.441 --> 00:26:18.679 line:-2 align:center
or reset and isn't even
stored on my own devices.


548
00:26:18,679 --> 00:26:21,148 align:center
Not only can this data
be used to serve ads


549
00:26:21,148 --> 00:26:23,350 align:center
on other sites that I visit,
it can be used


550
00:26:23,350 --> 00:26:25,385 align:center
to influence my behavior
without me knowing.


551
00:26:27,387 --> 00:26:29,456 align:center
Later on Sunday,
I started researching


552
00:26:29,456 --> 00:26:31,658 line:0
lawn mowers on Lawn Mower Site.


553
00:26:31,658 --> 00:26:34,494 line:0
Using my IP address and other
profile information,


554
00:26:34,494 --> 00:26:38,065 align:center
I was served an ad about
the couch that I looked at.


555
00:26:38,065 --> 00:26:39,933 align:center
Two days later,
I received a couch catalog


556
00:26:39,933 --> 00:26:42,469 align:center
in the mail
from Furniture Site.


557
00:26:42,469 --> 00:26:45,772 line:0
Internet tracking doesn't always
stay on the internet.


558
00:26:45,772 --> 00:26:47,174 align:center
With a detailed profile,


559
00:26:47,174 --> 00:26:50,344 line:0
tracking can transition
to physical space.


560
00:26:50,344 --> 00:26:52,679 line:0
Tracking reduces trust
and can lead people


561
00:26:52,679 --> 00:26:55,215 align:center
to limit what they do
on your website.


562
00:26:55,215 --> 00:26:58,218 align:center
Networks and equipment
makers are able to collect


563
00:26:58,218 --> 00:26:59,953 align:center
this type of information,
too,


564
00:26:59,953 --> 00:27:01,788 align:center
even discover behavior
patterns


565
00:27:01,788 --> 00:27:03,991 align:center
from people who
use your website or app.


566
00:27:05,526 --> 00:27:08,128 align:center
Technologies like TLS
and encrypted DNS


567
00:27:08,128 --> 00:27:11,098 align:center
help protect behavior patterns
and your users' data


568
00:27:11,098 --> 00:27:13,300 align:center
from being exposed
to network providers.


569
00:27:13,300 --> 00:27:15,936 line:0
You should
adopt these technologies.


570
00:27:15,936 --> 00:27:18,906 align:center
To learn more about how to use
